            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Variáveis são chamadas de variáveis porque os valores que elas armazenam podem mudar. Podemos atualizar <code>status</code> usando <code>=</code> e atribuindo um novo valor.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"status = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Watching Netflix&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"status = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Relaxing at the beach&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(status)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"35\" endIndex=\"36\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\":\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Relaxing at the beach\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>=</code>.</p></body></html>"
