            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Podemos adicionar valores de string juntos com um sinal de <code>+</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&quot;Followers:&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + \" /><text value=\"&quot;55&quot;\" class=\"string\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"13\" endIndex=\"14\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"-\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>+</code>.</p></body></html>"
